    "longBusinessSummary": "OPC Pharmaceutical Joint Stock Company engages in the processing, manufacturing, trading, importing, and exporting of traditional, herbal, and nature-based medicines in Vietnam and internationally. The company offers cardiovascular, nerve, vitamins and minerals, respiratory system, urinary, musculoskeletal system, external use, digestion, pain relief-inflammation, endocrine, and others drugs. It also offers health gifts; and nutrition products for health care, supplementing nutrients, nourishing the body, and boosting immunity. In addition, the company produces and trades in pharmaceutical products, medical supplies, machinery, medical equipment, chemicals, cosmetics, functional foods, and food products; and alcoholic beverages, carbonated drinks, and other beverages. In addition, it is involved in the cultivation, processing, and trading of medicinal plants. Further, the company provides scientific and technical consulting services and technology transfer services in the field of healthcare. OPC Pharmaceutical Joint Stock Company was founded in 1977 and is based in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam.",
